`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Reboot
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * reboot

 Reboot will shutdown the server. When the 'startup' (~/live/bin/startup)
script is used to control the server, a delay of fifteen seconds will ensue (to
allow old connections to die), and then the script will cause the server to
restart.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
